== 开发 ==
《使命召唤：黑色行动III》是[[決勝時刻系列|使命召唤系列]]的第12部正统续作，黑色行动系列的第三部作品。这也是第二款[[动视|动视]]以三年开发周期进行制作的游戏，第一款是[[使命召唤：高级战争|使命召唤：高级战争]]<ref name="Twitter">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/pcdev/status/594126768652423169|title=pcdev on Twitter: @treboruk92 Heavily modified from BO2 including completely new renderer|accessdate=2015-05-06|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193031/https://twitter.com/pcdev/status/594126768652423169|dead-url=no}}</ref>。开发团队（[[Infinity_Ward|Infinity Ward、]][[Treyarch|Treyarch]]和[[大锤游戏|大锤游戏]]）将用三年的开发时间制作每个使命召唤系列，而不是先前规定的两年。《黑色行动III》将使用以前《黑色行动II》用过的IW引擎的大幅修改的版本<ref name="Twitter"/>。

2015年6月9日，游戏的PlayStation 3和Xbox 360版本被证实正在由[[Beenox|Beenox]]和{{le|Mercenary Technology|Mercenary Technology}}开发。这些版本会缺少某些其他平台的模式，如游戏的战役模式<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://community.callofduty.com/community/call_of_duty/english/blackops3/blog/2015/09/25/new-details-for-ps3-and-xbox-360-versions-of-call-of-duty-black-ops-iii |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-09-26 |archive-date=2016-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326010435/https://community.callofduty.com/community/call_of_duty/english/blackops3/blog/2015/09/25/new-details-for-ps3-and-xbox-360-versions-of-call-of-duty-black-ops-iii |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/call-duty-black-ops-3-xbox-360-ps3/|title=Call of Duty: Black Ops 3 will get PS3 and Xbox 360 versions, too|first=Connor|last=Sheridan|work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|date=2015-06-09|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610091837/http://www.gamesradar.com/call-duty-black-ops-3-xbox-360-ps3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[美式橄欖球|美式橄榄球]]球队[[西雅图海鹰|西雅图海鹰]]的跑卫{{le|马肖恩·林奇|Marshawn Lynch}}将在《黑色行动III》中客串一个恶棍。Treyarch的制作人员马克·拉米亚（Mark Lamia）解释道工作室需要一个“威风的人物”，据悉林奇在大学和[[国家橄榄球联盟|国家橄榄球联盟]]生涯中曾是使命召唤系列狂热的粉丝<ref>{{cite web|title=Call of Duty goes "Beast Mode"|url=http://espn.go.com/nfl/story/_/id/13005815/black-ops-iii|last=Alipour|first=Sam|date=2015-06-09|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610131610/http://espn.go.com/nfl/story/_/id/13005815/black-ops-iii|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年6月15日，动视与[[索尼电脑娱乐|索尼电脑娱乐]]达成独占协定，未来《黑色行动III》所有的[[追加下载内容|追加下载内容]]将在PlayStation平台进行定时独占发布。这结束了从《[[使命召唤4：现代战争|使命召唤4：现代战争]]》开始的与[[微软|微软]]进行的类似的独家交易<ref name=polygon-sonycod>{{cite web|title='PlayStation is the new home of Call of Duty,' says PlayStation CEO on exclusive deal|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/15/8787135/call-of-duty-playstation-exclusive-deal-black-ops-3|website=Polygon|accessdate=2015-06-16|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214523/http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/15/8787135/call-of-duty-playstation-exclusive-deal-black-ops-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年8月18日，多人测试版在PlayStation 4平台发布<ref name="Playstation.com">{{cite web|url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2015/08/18/beta-guide-call-of-duty-black-ops-3-beta-live-now-on-ps4/|title=Call of Duty Black Ops 3 Beta: Everything You Need to Know|last=Shuman|first=Sid|publisher=playstation.com|date=2015-08-18|accessdate=2015-08-18|archive-date=2015-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150820132940/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2015/08/18/beta-guide-call-of-duty-black-ops-3-beta-live-now-on-ps4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，Xbox One和Windows平台于8月26日发布<ref name="BO3Trailer">{{cite web|title=Official Call of Duty: Black Ops III Reveal Trailer|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=58Pspqx0XGs|website=YouTube|publisher=Call of Duty|date=2015-04-26|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2019-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419071303/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=58Pspqx0XGs|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Eurogamer">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-04-26-call-of-duty-black-ops-3-pc-requirements-revealed|title=Call of Duty: Black Ops 3 PC requirements revealed|last=Robinson|first=Martin|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2015-04-26|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2018-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180812150935/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-04-26-call-of-duty-black-ops-3-pc-requirements-revealed|dead-url=no}}</ref>。所有版本的多人测试模式开放了6天。

